            98.2679443359375,
            543.3399047851562,
            129.31192016601562
          ],
          "text": "Master Direction on Penal Provisions in reporting of transactions/ balances at \nCurrency Chests",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            139.96795654296875,
            207.9972381591797,
            157.15194702148438
          ],
          "text": "1. Reporting Procedure",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            169.7879638671875,
            335.3761291503906,
            186.97195434570312
          ],
          "text": "1.1 Reporting of Currency Chest Transactions",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99993896484375,
            197.75999450683594,
            543.3358764648438,
            230.59201049804688
          ],
          "text": "The minimum amount of deposit into / withdrawal from currency chest shall be ₹1,00,000 \nand thereafter, in multiples of ₹50,000.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99993896484375,
            243.3480224609375,
            230.67718505859375,
            260.5320129394531
          ],
          "text": "1.2 Time limit for Reporting",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99993896484375,
            273.16802978515625,
            543.3370361328125,
            306.1920166015625
          ],
          "text": "1.2.1 The currency chests shall invariably report all transactions through CyM – CC portal \non the same day by 7 pm.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99998474121094,
            318.9480285644531,
            328.17596435546875,
            336.13201904296875
          ],
          "text": "1.2.2 Relaxation in respect of strike in banks",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b15",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            245.36990356445312,
            335.3825378417969,
            365.90631103515625,
            455.9189147949219
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            348.96002197265625,
            543.3370971679688,
            381.1800231933594
          ],
          "text": "Relaxation in the reporting period on account of strike situation shall be considered on \ncase-to-case basis.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996185302734,
            394.54803466796875,
            488.07598876953125,
            411.7320251464844
          ],
          "text": "2. Delayed Reporting / Wrong Reporting of Currency Chest Transactions",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            422.3880310058594,
            222.03599548339844,
            439.572021484375
          ],
          "text": "2.1 Levy of penal interest",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99998474121094,
            450.16802978515625,
            214.7159881591797,
            467.3520202636719
          ],
          "text": "2.1.1 Delay in Reporting",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99993896484375,
            478.02001953125,
            543.3399047851562,
            549.6600341796875
          ],
          "text": "In the event of delay in reporting currency chest transactions, penal interest at the rate \nindicated in paragraph 4 of this circular shall be levied on the amount due from the chest \nholding bank for the period of delay. Penal interest shall be calculated on T+0 basis i.e. \npenal interest shall be levied in respect of transactions not reported by currency chests \nto the Issue Office on the same business day within the time limit prescribed above.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99990844726562,
            560.927978515625,
            203.31593322753906,
            578.1119995117188
          ],
          "text": "2.1.2 Wrong Reporting",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b14",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99984741210938,
            588.8400268554688,
            543.3399047851562,
            701.8800048828125
          ],
          "text": "Penal interest shall be levied in respect of cases of wrong reporting in the same manner \ntill the date of receipt of corrected advice by Reserve Bank. As debits/credits to banks' \ncurrent accounts are raised on the basis of the transactions reported by the currency \nchests, penal interest shall invariably be levied in all cases of wrong reporting by the \ncurrency chests. It is expected that currency chests would ensure the correctness of \nfigures reported on the CyM - CC portal. Particular care shall be taken to ensure that \nremittances of fresh/re-issuable notes sent to the currency chests from RBI/Note printing \npresses are not reported as 'deposit' transactions.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
